The medical bed market can be segmented based on product type, technology, and end-user. In terms of product type, the market includes general medical beds, pediatric beds, birthing beds, bariatric beds, pressure relief beds, and others. Within the technology segment, medical beds can be categorized as powered beds, semi-electric beds, and manual beds. Lastly, the end-user segment comprises hospitals, home healthcare settings, elderly care facilities, and other healthcare institutions. These segments showcase the diverse applications and requirements within the medical bed market, catering to specific needs across different settings.

